long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds reactions to your google meet using the classic google meet chatbox! When you download it, adds a ton of icons to the bottom menu and when you press it, it tells you that it sent the reaction by showing it in the chatbox!
